  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13052896/levi_filler2.jpg" alt="LaplandShortBreak" data-udi="umb://media/6107d72c10114cc9bfb22de13fc20136" /></p>
<p>You can enjoy all that Lapland has to offer in just a few days, taking in the highlights of this snowy Landscape - from the Northern Lights, ski slopes to wildlife. </p>
<p>Select the best short break that works for you and enjoy a once-in-lifetime getaway that you will never forget. </p>
<h2>Short breaks to Saariselka</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Star Arctic Hotel - Northern Lights Discovery</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13068521/finland_saariselka_stararctic_glasscabinexterior.jpg" alt="StarArctic" data-udi="umb://media/2b396af07012459cbcb794618683a19a" /></p>
<p>Perched atop Kaunispää Fell in Saariselkä, the Star Arctic is a modern and stylish hotel with spacious Lappish-style suites.</p>
<p><strong>What's included - </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights &amp; transfers from London Gatwick airport to Ivalo​ airport</li>
<li>3 or 4 nights' stay at the Star Arctic Hotel​</li>
<li>Full board meals​</li>
<li>Winter outdoor thermal clothing and boots​</li>
<li>Four arctic excursions included: Husky sleigh ride, Reindeer visit, Snowmobile safari and Aurora hunt by car​</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Please note:</em> Available January and February 2025. Our 3-night package runs from Tuesday to Friday (available for adults 12years+). Our 4-night package runs from Friday to Tuesday (available for families with children aged 5years+). ​</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/resorts/laplandfinland/saariselka/star-arctic-northern-lights-discovery" class="c-btn">Star Arctic short breaks</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Juutua Arctic Hotel - Aurora Adventure</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13107169/wilderness_hotel_juutua_finland_sauna_northern_lights.jpg" alt="JuutuaHotelShortBreak" data-udi="umb://media/7a91b1346203428cb2c4812a98429c41" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>Located along the shores of Juutua River in the Sámi Village Inari, this hotel offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and authentic Lappish charm.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>What's included - </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights and transfers from London Gatwick airport to Ivalo ​​airport</li>
<li>3 or 4 nights’ stay at the Wilderness Hotel Juutua ​​</li>
<li>Full board meals ​</li>
<li>Winter outdoor thermal clothing and boots​</li>
<li>3 night stays include: a snowmobile safari, husky safari, aurora camp, aurora workshop, a visit to Siida Saami museum and an arctic sauna and jacuzzi experience. ​</li>
<li>4 night stays include: a snowmobile safari with lunch, husky safari, aurora camp, meet the reindeer and a gentle snowshoe trip.​</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Please note:</em> Available December 2024 – February 2025. Our 3-night package runs from Tuesday to Friday and our 4-night package runs from Friday to Tuesday.​</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/resorts/laplandfinland/saariselka/juutua-arctic-aurora-adventure" title="Juutua Hotel short breaks" class="c-btn">Juutua hotel short breaks</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Short breaks to Levi</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Panorama Hotel - Festive escape</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13107300/panorama_hotel_levi_hotel_exterior_evening-900.jpg" alt="PanoramaHotel" data-udi="umb://media/ec92fe2429ee401284c9dbcf55e04eb6" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Enjoy an Arctic escape this Christmas on a short break, staying at the Panorama Hotel &amp; Apartments. It's slopeside position is unmatched, with incredible views across Levi village.</p>
<p><strong>What's included - </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights and transfers to Kittilä Airport from London Gatwick, Manchester or Bristol</li>
<li>3 or 4 night's stay at the Panorama Hotel &amp; Apartments</li>
<li>Half board meals</li>
<li>Festive Feast on your final evening (this replaces your last half board dinner)</li>
<li>Express gondola tickets linking the hotel to Levi village (excludes first or last day)</li>
<li>Choose from pre-bookable optional excursions like Snowmobiling, Santa's Elves Hideaway and a Combined Husky and Reindeer Safari.</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Please note:</em> Departing between 01 - 18th December 2024. Guests staying 4 nights also have the option to add a Luxury Glass Igloo Overnight Stay or a Ski Taster</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4d944e9092f1422bbf24362acef18af5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4d944e9092f1422bbf24362acef18af5}" title="Panorama Hotel &amp; Apartments (Short Break)" class="c-btn">Panorama Hotel short breaks</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Northern Lights adventure</h3>
<br /><img style="width: 500px; height: 500px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13095231/inghams-lapland-893-adobestock_413147056.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500" alt="NorthernLightsAdventure" data-udi="umb://media/fed9c95745ed4372bd85e0f95a894a9d" />
<p>If seeing the Northern Lights is on your bucket list, then book one of our Lapland holidays specifically designed around this famous natural wonder.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights" class="c-btn">Northern Lights</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Santa Breaks short holidays</h3>
<br /><img style="width: 500px; height: 500px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13098868/santa-and-sleigh-500x500.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500" alt="SantaBreakHolidays" data-udi="umb://media/96bedb9caab8468d96fa1370bbac4297" />
<p>If you want to visit Lapland on a short break but are looking to meet the man himself, Santa, then we have the perfect itinerary for you and your family.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks" class="c-btn">Santa Breaks</a></div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays" class="c-btn">Lapland holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Lapland deals</a></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
